{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/cantika-kisah-tragis-putri-ilmuwan-khilaf/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Cantika: Kisah Tragis Putri Ilmuwan Khilaf","content":"<p>Bro sis udah pada baca komik Indonesia <em>online</em> Cantika belum? Buat yang belum tahu nih, Cantika ini adalah komik digital Indonesia yang dapat dibaca di situs komik Indonesia dan situs tersebut merupakan situs komik <em>online</em> gratis yang dibut oleh CIAYO Comics. Cantika adalah salah satu komik <em>thriller online </em>di CIAYO Comics. Komik seru ini menceritakan pergulatan batin seorang anak perempuan akan kenyataan yang dihadapi, serta masalah rumit dua pria yang berbuah kejadian di luar nalar. Kalo mau baca cerita lengkapnya, langsung aja mampir ke CIAYO Comics. Sekarang kita kenalin tokoh-tokoh utamanya ya…</p>\n<p><strong>Cantika</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_685\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-685\" data-attachment-id=\"685\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/cantika-kisah-tragis-putri-ilmuwan-khilaf/attachment/cantika6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cantika6\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: ciayo.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-685\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika6.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: ciayo.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-685\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: ciayo.com</p></div>\n<p>Anak perempuan ini bernama Cantika. Ia sudah tinggal dengan Heru sejak kecil, dan memanggilnya dengan sebutan ayah. Ia sangat menyayangi Heru. Meski masih sangat muda, dia suka memasak. Karena ditinggal ibunya dari kecil, dia tumbuh menjadi anak yang mandiri dan cekatan saat membantu menyelesaikan pekerjaan rumah, seperti bersih-bersih. Ia tipe anak yang tegar dan cukup kuat menghadapi berbagai permasalahan meski umurnya masih 10 tahun.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_687\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-687\" data-attachment-id=\"687\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/cantika-kisah-tragis-putri-ilmuwan-khilaf/attachment/cantika5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cantika5\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: ciayo.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-687\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika5.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: ciayo.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-687\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: ciayo.com</p></div>\n<p>Meski Cantika cukup tegar, bukan berarti ia tidak pernah menangis. Saat dilanda kesedihan, ia menumpahkannya lewat tangisan. Siapapun akan pilu melihatnya menangis. Ia paling tidak suka saat orang yang tiba-tiba hadir di hidupnya menyakiti keluarga atau orang-orang kesayangannya.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_688\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-688\" data-attachment-id=\"688\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/cantika-kisah-tragis-putri-ilmuwan-khilaf/attachment/cantika2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cantika2\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: ciayo.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-688\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika2.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: ciayo.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-688\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: ciayo.com</p></div>\n<p>Pria ini bernama Heru. Ia tinggal bersama Cantika sejak anak perempuan itu dilahirkan. Pria 38 tahun ini adalah salah satu ilmuwan di sebuah proyek penelitian. Namun sebuah kejadian di masa lalu, membuat Heru terkena imbasnya.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_689\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-689\" data-attachment-id=\"689\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/cantika-kisah-tragis-putri-ilmuwan-khilaf/attachment/cantika1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cantika1\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-689\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika1.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: ciayo.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-689\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: ciayo.com</p></div>\n<p>Heru mengalami kenyataan pahit yang sulit diterima akal sehat. Kondisinya itu, membuat Heru harus menjaga jarak dengan Cantika. Demi keselamatan Cantika, Heru menitipkan anak perempuan itu pada Gunawan.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_690\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-690\" data-attachment-id=\"690\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/cantika-kisah-tragis-putri-ilmuwan-khilaf/attachment/cantika4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cantika4\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: ciayo.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-690\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika4.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: ciayo.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-690\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: ciayo.com</p></div>\n<p>Bisa dikatakan, Gunawan adalah biang dari kondisi yang dialami Heru. Akibat dirundung dendam, pria 40 tahun ini melakukan tindakan yang cukup brutal. Perbuatannya di masa lalu ternyata mengorbankan rekan kerjanya.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_691\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-691\" data-attachment-id=\"691\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/cantika-kisah-tragis-putri-ilmuwan-khilaf/attachment/cantika3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cantika3\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-691\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika3.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: ciayo.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Cantika3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-691\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: ciayo.com</p></div>\n<p>Setelah hilang kontak dengan rekan kerjanya, ternyata dendam masih bersemayam di benak Gunawan. Bahkan, pertemuan pun tidak membuat masalahnya menemui jalan keluar. Malah, kenyataan yang ada membuatnya semakin frustasi dan kebingungan.</p>\n<p>Hubungan rumit antara Heru, Gunawan, dan Cantika mulai terbongkar setelah mereka bertemu kembali. Bagaimana kelanjutan ceritanya? Langsung aja baca <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/comic/cantika\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Cantika</a>!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"88d2148a-5f17-532d-b753-460bcaade0ca"}}}